text: Liannes Castañeda Simon (born 18 October 1986) is a Cuban volleyball player. She played at the 2011 FIVB World Grand Prix and 2012 FIVB World Grand Prix. She also played for VK Prostějov and Cignal HD Spikers. == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players
